attributes.description: Overview of Cisco Meraki Device Health metrics

query.esql:
from metrics-cisco_meraki_metrics.device_health-* 
| keep meraki.device.serial, meraki.device.license.expiration_date 
| where meraki.device.license.expiration_date is not null 
| stats expiration_date=max(meraki.device.license.expiration_date) by meraki.device.serial 
| sort expiration_date desc 
| rename meraki.device.serial AS `Device Serial`, expiration_date AS `Expiration Date`

from metrics-cisco_meraki_metrics.device_health-* 
| keep meraki.device.serial, meraki.device.license.expiration_date 
| where meraki.device.license.expiration_date is not null 
| stats expiration_date=max(meraki.device.license.expiration_date) by meraki.device.serial 
| sort expiration_date desc 
| rename meraki.device.serial AS `Device Serial`, expiration_date AS `Expiration Date`

attributes.title: [Metrics Cisco Meraki] Device Health Overview
